Put the lines below in context.xml in tomcat_base/conf (make sure the db and user exist and the user has permissions for the db)

<Resource name="jdbc/practit"
auth="Container"
type="javax.sql.DataSource"
username="battleshipsUser"
password="Internship1"
driverClassName="net.sourceforge.jtds.jdbc.Driver"
url="jdbc:jtds:sqlserver:/localhost:1433/practit"
maxActive="8"
maxIdle="4"/>




